        #### Examples
        delete orphaned repos (if basename = repo name)
        
        ```bash
        $ cd ~/git/owner
        $ python -m github_repos | awk -F '/' '{print $2}' | grep -v -iF "$(ls -1)" | xargs python -m github_delete
        ```
        
